data.description: Welcome to your future home in beautiful Winter Haven, Florida! This spacious and inviting property boasts 4 bedrooms, and 2 bathrooms, and is adorned with elegant tile flooring throughout the main areas and master bedroom. Enjoy the luxury of no rear neighbors, providing you with added privacy and tranquility. Step outside and be surrounded by the natural beauty of Florida.  What's more, this home has a brand new roof (September '23 and solar panels installed, offering you energy efficiency and peace of mind.  Conveniently located close to Highway 27, you're just a stone's throw away from restaurants, shopping, and all the conveniences you need. Plus, the magic of Disney World and the exciting attractions of Orlando are only 40 minutes away, offering endless entertainment possibilities.  Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity. Schedule your showing today and make this your next dream home!
